WEBVTT

00:01:29.433 --> 00:01:34.276
Her heart was truly broken,
and she now faced yet another recovery.

00:01:34.959 --> 00:01:37.515
But five months after the breakup,

00:01:37.539 --> 00:01:40.734
Kathy still couldn't stop
thinking about Rich.

00:01:40.758 --> 00:01:43.372
Her heart was still very much broken.

00:01:44.126 --> 00:01:45.303
The question is:

00:01:45.786 --> 00:01:47.220
Why?

00:01:47.244 --> 00:01:51.340
Why was this incredibly strong
and determined woman

00:01:51.364 --> 00:01:54.272
unable to marshal the same
emotional resources

00:01:54.296 --> 00:01:57.715
that got her through four years
of cancer treatments?

00:01:58.619 --> 00:02:00.898
Why do so many of us flounder